{"source":"recieeGmwbblVWK8u","target":"recsU2ZSdzBvDqzgI","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recieeGmwbblVWK8u","target":"recDWNfN3f6E04V4m","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recieeGmwbblVWK8u","target":"recoBhapSAf2zo3UV","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recieeGmwbblVWK8u","target":"rec3RF6Fb7wZUoamW","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recieeGmwbblVWK8u","target":"rec3w84nsjQvkJEE3","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recieeGmwbblVWK8u","target":"rec81f3wE4gATsRRE","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recieeGmwbblVWK8u","target":"rec3gWYVMktOUkAzZ","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recieeGmwbblVWK8u","target":"recFF06mG50AJliKz","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recieeGmwbblVWK8u","target":"recL1WV82pXaRBQ59","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recieeGmwbblVWK8u","target":"recKRsEFLaEueJvei","label":"event"},{"source":"recieeGmwbblVWK8u","target":"rec9JB5FY6jMOyEY3","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recpUFtPJpeGDPQiO","ref":"1Sam.17.1","text":"Now the Philistines gathered together their armies to battle, and were gathered together at Shochoh, which belongeth to Judah, and pitched between Shochoh and Azekah, in Ephesdammim.","year":-1063},{"id":"recAZcYmR7AVQmCfq","ref":"1Sam.17.2","text":"And Saul and the men of Israel were gathered together, and pitched by the valley of Elah, and set the battle in array against the Philistines.","year":-1063},{"id":"recbHUOAo1vp8synb","ref":"1Sam.17.3","text":"And the Philistines stood on a mountain on the one side, and Israel stood on a mountain on the other side: and there was a valley between them.","year":-1063},{"id":"recxJ00lswVbgSa9C","ref":"1Sam.17.4","text":"And there went out a champion out of the camp of the Philistines, named Goliath, of Gath, whose height was six cubits and a span.","year":-1063},{"id":"recyCulFfiSNldJsH","ref":"1Sam.17.5","text":"And he had an helmet of brass upon his head, and he was armed with a coat of mail; and the weight of the coat was five thousand shekels of brass.","year":-1063},{"id":"rec5aPdkseVbuEkAd","ref":"1Sam.17.6","text":"And he had greaves of brass upon his legs, and a target of brass between his shoulders.","year":-1063},{"id":"rec5qQu1mVVCu8bjE","ref":"1Sam.17.7","text":"And the staff of his spear was like a weaver’s beam; and his spear’s head weighed six hundred shekels of iron: and one bearing a shield went before him.","year":-1063},{"id":"recSKGDDFbbF08Ror","ref":"1Sam.17.8","text":"And he stood and cried unto the armies of Israel, and said unto them, Why are ye come out to set your battle in array? am not I a Philistine, and ye servants to Saul? choose you a man for you, and let him come down to me.","year":-1063}]}
